## Choosing a License

### For Users
If you're using this software:
1. **Prefer Hippocratic License 3.0** if you can commit to ethical use principles
2. Use Apache 2.0 if you need patent protection
3. Use MIT if you need maximum permissiveness

### For Contributors
By contributing to this project, you agree that your contributions will be licensed under the same multi-license structure, allowing users to choose their preferred license option.

### For Questions
If you have questions about licensing or need clarification on which license applies to your use case, please open an issue in the repository.

